 Bastogne, 12/19-31/44<br />Breaking point; Bastogne, 1/1-13/45 <br />Attack; Noville, 1/14-17/45<br />Patrol: Haguenau, 1/18-2/23/45<br />"Best feeling in the world": Mourmelon, 2/25-4/2/45<br />Getting to know the enemy: Germany, 4/2-30/45<br />Drinking Hitler's champagne; Berchtesgaden, 5/1-8/45<br />Soldier's dream life; Austria, 5/8-7/31/45<br />Postwar careers; 1945-91<br />Acknowledgments &amp; Sources<br />Index</span></div></div></div></div><div data-testid="genresList" class="BookPageMetadataSection__genres"><ul class="CollapsableList" aria-label="Top genres for this book"><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genre"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/history" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">History</span></a></span> <span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genre"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/non-fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Nonfiction</span></a></span> <span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genre"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/war" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">War</span></a></span> <span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genre"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/military-fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Military Fiction</span></a></span> <div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium" aria-label="Show all items in the list"><span class="Button__labelItem">...more</span></button></div></ul></div><div class="BookDetails"><div class="CollapsableList"><span class="Text Text__body3"><div class="FeaturedDetails"><p data-testid="pagesFormat">432 pages, Paperback</p><p data-testid="publicationInfo">First published June 6, 1992</p></div></span> <div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small" aria-label="Show more bo